name: TurboTax Canada 2013 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .TT13 files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: TT13 files contain tax information for the 2013 tax year, which means they are typically created in 2014. When you complete a tax return in TurboTax, you can file it within the program or print and mail the official tax forms.
NOTE: The previous version of TurboTax Canada (2012) saved files with a .TT12 file extension.
